    '| `salvador_vault` (keeper) | `knowledge_audit`, `knowledge_health`, `knowledge_merge`, `knowledge_reorganize` |',
    '| `salvador_vault` (mgmt) | `vault_get`, `vault_update`, `vault_remove`, `vault_tags`, `vault_domains`, `vault_recent` |',
    '| `salvador_curator` | `curator_status`, `curator_detect_duplicates`, `curator_contradictions`, `curator_groom_all`, `curator_consolidate`, `curator_health_audit` |',
    '| `salvador_curator` (advanced) | `curator_enrich`, `curator_hybrid_contradictions`, `curator_entry_history`, `curator_queue_stats` |',
    '| `salvador_plan` | `create_plan`, `approve_plan`, `plan_split`, `plan_reconcile`, `plan_complete_lifecycle` |',
