    '| `salvador_brain` | `brain_stats`, `brain_feedback`, `rebuild_vocabulary`, `brain_strengths`, `brain_recommend` |',
    '| `salvador_memory` | `memory_search`, `memory_capture`, `session_capture` |',
    '| `salvador_control` | `route_intent`, `morph`, `get_behavior_rules`, `governance_dashboard`, `governance_policy` |',
    '| `salvador_loop` | `loop_start`, `loop_iterate`, `loop_status`, `loop_cancel` |',
